186    /**
187     * check if user owns the project
188     * or if the project is shared with the user
189     *
190     * @param string $userid
191     * @param string $projectid
192     * @return bool
193     */
194    public function userCanAccessProject(string $userid, string $projectid): bool {
195        $projectInfo = $this->getProjectInfo($projectid);
196        if ($projectInfo !== null) {
197            // does the user own the project ?
198            if ($projectInfo['userid'] === $userid) {
199                return true;
200            } else {
201                $qb = $this->db->getQueryBuilder();
202                // is the project shared with the user ?
203                $qb->select('userid', 'projectid')
204                    ->from('cospend_shares', 's')
205                    ->where(
206                        $qb->expr()->eq('type', $qb->createNamedParameter(Application::SHARE_TYPE_USER, IQueryBuilder::PARAM_STR))
207                    )
208                    ->andWhere(
209                        $qb->expr()->eq('projectid', $qb->createNamedParameter($projectid, IQueryBuilder::PARAM_STR))
210                    )
211                    ->andWhere(
212                        $qb->expr()->eq('userid', $qb->createNamedParameter($userid, IQueryBuilder::PARAM_STR))
213                    );
214                $req = $qb->executeQuery();
215                $dbProjectId = null;
216                while ($row = $req->fetch()) {
217                    $dbProjectId = $row['projectid'];
218                    break;
219                }
220                $req->closeCursor();
221                $qb = $qb->resetQueryParts();
222
223                if ($dbProjectId !== null) {
224                    return true;
225                } else {
226                    // if not, is the project shared with a group containing the user?
227                    $userO = $this->userManager->get($userid);
228                    $accessWithGroup = null;
229
230                    $qb->select('userid')
231                        ->from('cospend_shares', 's')
232                        ->where(
233                            $qb->expr()->eq('type', $qb->createNamedParameter(Application::SHARE_TYPE_GROUP, IQueryBuilder::PARAM_STR))
234                        )
235                        ->andWhere(
236                            $qb->expr()->eq('projectid', $qb->createNamedParameter($projectid, IQueryBuilder::PARAM_STR))
237                        );
238                    $req = $qb->executeQuery();
239                    while ($row = $req->fetch()) {
240                        $groupId = $row['userid'];
241                        if ($this->groupManager->groupExists($groupId) && $this->groupManager->get($groupId)->inGroup($userO)) {
242                            $accessWithGroup = $groupId;
243                            break;
244                        }
245                    }
246                    $req->closeCursor();
247                    $qb = $qb->resetQueryParts();
248
249                    if ($accessWithGroup !== null) {
250                        return true;

319

322                }

344                    }

347                $qb = $qb->resetQueryParts();

683    /**

698    public function getProjectStatistics(string $projectId, ?string $memberOrder = null, ?int $tsMin = null, ?int $tsMax = null,
699                                          ?string $paymentMode = null, ?int $category = null, ?float $amountMin = null, ?float $amountMax = null,
700                                          bool $showDisabled = true, ?int $currencyId = null): array {
701        $timeZone = $this->dateTimeZone->getTimeZone();
702        $membersWeight = [];

735            }
736            $membersPaidFor['total'][$memberId] = 0.0;
737        }
738
739        // build list of members to display
740        $membersToDisplay = [];
741        $allMembersIds = [];
742        foreach ($members as $member) {
743            $memberId = $member['id'];
744            $allMembersIds[] = $memberId;
745            // only take enabled members or those with non-zero balance
